def load_data(path):
    data = pd.read_csv(path, index_col=0)
    data.index = pd.to_datetime(data.index)
    return data

mean_pw_edge_list_5_normal = net_5.groupby('country').median().reset_index().melt(id_vars = ['country'],  var_name = 'source', value_name = 'weight')
mean_pw_edge_list_50_normal = net_50.groupby('country').median().reset_index().melt(id_vars = ['country'],  var_name = 'source', value_name = 'weight')

# mean_pw_edge_list_5_normal = net_5.swaplevel(0,1).loc['2006-12-01':'2008-09-01'].swaplevel(0,1).groupby('country').median().reset_index().melt(id_vars = ['country'],  var_name = 'source', value_name = 'weight')
# mean_pw_edge_list_50_normal = net_50.swaplevel(0,1).loc['2006-12-01':'2008-09-01'].swaplevel(0,1).groupby('country').median().reset_index().melt(id_vars = ['country'],  var_name = 'source', value_name = 'weight')


mean_pw_edge_list_5_crisis = net_5.swaplevel(0,1).loc['2008-12-01':'2009-12-01'].swaplevel(0,1).groupby('country').median().reset_index().melt(id_vars = ['country'],  var_name = 'source', value_name = 'weight')
mean_pw_edge_list_50_crisis = net_50.swaplevel(0,1).loc['2008-12-01':'2009-12-01'].swaplevel(0,1).groupby('country').median().reset_index().melt(id_vars = ['country'],  var_name = 'source', value_name = 'weight')


mean_pw_network_5_normal = nx.from_pandas_edgelist(mean_pw_edge_list_5_normal, source =  'source', target = 'country', edge_attr = ['weight'], create_using = nx.DiGraph)
mean_pw_network_50_normal = nx.from_pandas_edgelist(mean_pw_edge_list_50_normal, source =  'source', target = 'country', edge_attr = ['weight'], create_using = nx.DiGraph)
mean_pw_network_5_crisis = nx.from_pandas_edgelist(mean_pw_edge_list_5_crisis, source =  'source', target = 'country', edge_attr = ['weight'], create_using = nx.DiGraph)
mean_pw_network_50_crisis = nx.from_pandas_edgelist(mean_pw_edge_list_50_crisis, source =  'source', target = 'country', edge_attr = ['weight'], create_using = nx.DiGraph)


weights_5_normal, weights_50_normal = nx.get_edge_attributes(mean_pw_network_5_normal,'weight').values(), nx.get_edge_attributes(mean_pw_network_50_normal,'weight').values()
weights_5_crisis, weights_50_crisis = nx.get_edge_attributes(mean_pw_network_5_crisis,'weight').values(), nx.get_edge_attributes(mean_pw_network_50_crisis,'weight').values()

minn_normal, maxx_normal =  min(min(weights_5_normal),min(weights_50_normal)), max(max(weights_5_normal),max(weights_50_normal))
minn_crisis, maxx_crisis =  min(min(weights_5_crisis),min(weights_50_crisis)), max(max(weights_5_crisis),max(weights_50_crisis))

minn, maxx = min(minn_normal, minn_crisis),  max(maxx_normal, maxx_crisis)
fig, axs = plt.subplots(2,2, figsize = (16,16))

nx.draw_networkx(mean_pw_network_5_normal, pos=nx.shell_layout(mean_pw_network_5_normal), ax = axs[0,0], node_color = '#000000',font_color = '#ffffff', node_size = 800, style = 'dashdot', arrowsize=20,edge_color = weights_5_normal,edge_cmap=plt.cm.Blues, edge_vmin = minn, edge_vmax=maxx)
nx.draw_networkx(mean_pw_network_50_normal, pos=nx.shell_layout(mean_pw_network_50_normal), ax = axs[0,1], node_color = '#000000',font_color = '#ffffff', node_size = 800, style = 'dashdot', arrowsize=20,edge_color = weights_50_normal,edge_cmap=plt.cm.Blues, edge_vmin = minn, edge_vmax=maxx)
nx.draw_networkx(mean_pw_network_5_crisis, pos=nx.shell_layout(mean_pw_network_5_crisis), ax = axs[1,0], node_color = '#000000',font_color = '#ffffff', node_size = 800, style = 'dashdot', arrowsize=20,edge_color = weights_5_crisis,edge_cmap=plt.cm.Reds, edge_vmin = minn, edge_vmax=maxx)
nx.draw_networkx(mean_pw_network_50_crisis, pos=nx.shell_layout(mean_pw_network_50_crisis), ax = axs[1,1], node_color = '#000000',font_color = '#ffffff', node_size = 800, style = 'dashdot', arrowsize=20,edge_color = weights_50_crisis,edge_cmap=plt.cm.Reds, edge_vmin = minn, edge_vmax=maxx)

sum_5_normal, sum_50_normal = round(mean_pw_edge_list_5_normal['weight'].sum(),2), round(mean_pw_edge_list_50_normal['weight'].sum(),2)
sum_5_crisis, sum_50_crisis = round(mean_pw_edge_list_5_crisis['weight'].sum(),2), round(mean_pw_edge_list_50_crisis['weight'].sum(),2)

s  = "Sum of median pairwise connectedness: {}"

axs[0,0].text(0.5, 0, s.format(sum_5_normal), fontsize = 16,  horizontalalignment='center', verticalalignment='center', transform=axs[0,0].transAxes)
axs[0,1].text(0.5, 0, s.format(sum_50_normal), fontsize = 16, horizontalalignment='center', verticalalignment='center', transform=axs[0,1].transAxes)
axs[1,0].text(0.5, 0, s.format(sum_5_crisis), fontsize = 16, horizontalalignment='center', verticalalignment='center', transform=axs[1,0].transAxes)
axs[1,1].text(0.5, 0, s.format(sum_50_crisis), fontsize = 16, horizontalalignment='center', verticalalignment='center', transform=axs[1,1].transAxes)

for ax in axs:
    for i in ax:
        i.axis('off')

axs[0,0].set_title(u'1992-2016  \n Median Pairwise directional Connectedness [5th Quantile]', fontsize = 14)

fig = plt.figure(figsize = (25,8))

fifth  =(net_5.abs()).groupby('date').apply(lambda x: np.median(x.values.ravel()))
fiftieth = (net_50.abs()).groupby('date').apply(lambda x:np.median(x.values.ravel()))

print stats.ttest_ind(fifth,fiftieth)

plt.plot(fifth.index[26:],fifth[26:], label = '5th Quantile', linestyle = '-', linewidth = 1.5, c = 'r')
plt.plot(fiftieth.index[26:],fiftieth[26:], label = '50th Quantile', linestyle = '-', linewidth = 1.5, c = 'k')

plt.title('MEDIAN PAIRWISE CONNECTEDNESS', fontsize = 30)
plt.xlabel("Quarter", fontsize = 20)
plt.ylabel("Median Pairwise Connectedness", fontsize = 20)
plt.legend()

plt.tight_layout(pad=3.0)
plt.savefig('graphs/F1O1_Aggregate_{}.png'.format('Total_Pairwise__Connectedness'))

Ttest_indResult(statistic=7.571093407615457, pvalue=1.5630901397318222e-12)

CENTRALITY CALCULATION¶

CENTRALITY OF 5TH¶

In [23]:
centrality = []
for date in net_5.index.get_level_values(1):
    net_data = net_5.xs(date, level=1, drop_level=True)

    net = net_data.reset_index().melt(id_vars = ['country'],  var_name = 'source', value_name = 'weight')
    net = nx.from_pandas_edgelist(net, source =  'source', target = 'country', edge_attr = ['weight'], create_using = nx.DiGraph)

    centrality_t = nx.katz_centrality(net, weight = 'weight')
    centrality.append(centrality_t)
centrality = pd.DataFrame(centrality, index = net_5.index.get_level_values(1))

centrality.plot(figsize = (25,8))
plt.title(u'KATZ CENTRALITY SCORE FOR 5th QUANTILE NETWORKS', fontsize = 30)
plt.xlabel("Quarters", fontsize = 13)
plt.ylabel("Katz Centrality Score", fontsize = 13)
plt.legend(bbox_to_anchor=(1.005, 1), loc=2, borderaxespad=0)

plt.tight_layout(pad=3.0)
plt.savefig('graphs/F1O1_Aggregate_{}.png'.format('Katz_Centrality_5th'))

fig, axs = plt.subplots(1,2, figsize = (25,6))
